    "m_Content": "FadeStart and fade end adjust the gradient ratio for the shader\n\nfade start must be lower than fade end\n\nstart = .1 \nend = .9\ngives a very gradual grade\n\nstart = .6\nend = .9\ngives a sharper grade",
